com.simsilica.ethereal

Class IdIndex

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simsilica.ethereal.IdIndex

  • public class IdIndex
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides a unique limited range set of integer IDs for a set of Long object IDs. Generated IDs can be reused later if the caller returns them to the pool with retireId().
